a delicious recipe.

00:05:19.934 --> 00:05:21.850
You've got your ingredients
which is your part

00:05:21.850 --> 00:05:25.042
numbers, or your parts, right?

00:05:25.042 --> 00:05:29.040
You have a process
that you're following.

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:32.860
And at the end of it you
should have something special,

00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:35.140
something delicious,
something wholesome,

00:05:35.140 --> 00:05:39.100
something that is greater
than the sum of the parts.

00:05:39.100 --> 00:05:41.960
