continues to emerge and grow,

00:13:45.350 --> 00:13:48.200
the problems that we are
being asked to tackle,

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:51.330
the technologies
at our disposal,

00:13:51.330 --> 00:13:54.290
the opportunities for
wonderful outcomes,

00:13:54.290 --> 00:13:59.000
the dangers and risks of
unintended consequences--

