be PDR, Polygyny Design Review.

00:37:02.250 --> 00:37:05.070
That's when the concept, the
architecture, the high level

00:37:05.070 --> 00:37:08.910
decomposition of the system,
the assignment of functions

00:37:08.910 --> 00:37:14.410
to those chunks at level one or
