And you see the
balloon in our logo.

01:09:08.050 --> 01:09:10.949
And we're not going to
do the balloon right now,

01:09:10.949 --> 01:09:14.990
but the first mission will
just be the rover itself.

01:09:14.990 --> 01:09:18.380
