We don't have to go fast.

01:13:27.360 --> 01:13:33.030
We have weeks or months to be
there, so one kilometer per day

01:13:33.030 --> 01:13:35.510
is just fine.

01:13:35.510 --> 01:13:38.810
There should be for
a scientific payload.

01:13:38.810 --> 01:13:42.180
Room means physical
space and also

