01:18:12.990 --> 01:18:13.490
this.

01:18:13.490 --> 01:18:16.700
And if it will be too
high then 3.3 volts,

01:18:16.700 --> 01:18:20.590
it will [INAUDIBLE] it again
with charging the battery.

01:18:20.590 --> 01:18:23.310
And that was basically
the main concept

01:18:23.310 --> 01:18:27.060
that he implemented then.

