So what we could have
done was this [INAUDIBLE]

01:20:27.260 --> 01:20:32.370
metrics, or the further points,
to optimize this design,

01:20:32.370 --> 01:20:36.540
but we figured out that
kind of without this,

01:20:36.540 --> 01:20:39.950
we just decided, kind of, to
take one of these options,

01:20:39.950 --> 01:20:40.450
I think.

